    "116432445": {
      "title": "Modular forms of weight 1/2",
      "abstract": "We will construct θ-series of weight 1/2 and 3/2 for some congruence subgroups of SL(2,ℤ) by taking appropriate coefficients of the representation \\( \\mathop{R}\\limits^{\\sim } \\) of SL(2;ℝ), illustrating the method sketched in 2.3. Our method will be the following: ::: ::: 1) ::: ::: Analyze the possible lowest weight vectors in the Shale-Weil representation \\( \\mathop{R}\\limits^{\\sim } \\) of \\( \\mathop{G}\\limits^{\\sim } \\) ::: ::: ::: ::: ::: 2) ::: ::: For a given congruence subgroup Γ of SL(2,ℤ), produce some semi-invariant linear functionals under Γ, using the model H = H(r, x) of the representation W."
    }
